{"body": "The repeal of any provision of the Personal Income Tax Law shall not affect any act done or any right accruing or accrued, or any suit or proceeding had or commenced in any civil cause, before such repeal; but all rights and liabilities under such law shall continue, and may be enforced in the same manner, as if such repeal had not been made.", "citation_label": "us ca code rtc p4 2", "citation_path": "us-ca/statute/rtc/17029/block-2", "document_class": "statute", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "17029.", "id": "ac50a5b3-1e21-5bfe-96ec-f796b465578e", "jurisdiction": "us-ca", "kind": "block", "language": "en", "level": 2, "metadata": {"block_count": 2, "content_type": null, "download_url": "https://leginfo.legislature.ca.gov/faces/codes_displaySection.xhtml?lawCode=RTC&sectionNum=17029.", "fetched_at": "2026-07-14T01:42:23Z", "kind": "block", "recovery_parser": "state-statutes:california", "source_url": "https://leginfo.legislature.ca.gov/faces/codes_displaySection.xhtml?lawCode=RTC&sectionNum=17029.", "title": "us ca code rtc p4"}, "ordinal": 2, "parent_citation_path": "us-ca/statute/rtc/17029", "parent_id": "fd1b5028-8fec-5044-9a76-a2a607ba2227", "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_format": "html", "source_id": "us-ca-code-rtc-p4", "source_path": "sources/us-ca/statute/2026-07-13-recovery/official-documents/us-ca-code-rtc-p4", "source_url": "https://leginfo.legislature.ca.gov/faces/codes_displaySection.xhtml?lawCode=RTC&sectionNum=17029.", "version": "2026-07-13-recovery"}
