{"body": "Unless otherwise specifically provided therein, the provisions of any act:\n\n(a) That affect the imposition or computation of taxes, additions to tax, penalties, or the allowance of credits against the tax, shall be applied to taxable years beginning on or after January 1 of the year in which the act takes effect.\n\n(b) That otherwise affect the provisions of this part shall be applied on and after the date the act takes effect.", "citation_label": "us ca code rtc p5 2", "citation_path": "us-ca/statute/rtc/17034/block-2", "document_class": "statute", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "17034.", "id": "23015d61-1327-52b7-9d2e-1def94f857d8", "jurisdiction": "us-ca", "kind": "block", "language": "en", "level": 2, "metadata": {"block_count": 2, "content_type": null, "download_url": "https://leginfo.legislature.ca.gov/faces/codes_displaySection.xhtml?lawCode=RTC&sectionNum=17034.", "fetched_at": "2026-07-14T01:42:23Z", "kind": "block", "recovery_parser": "state-statutes:california", "source_url": "https://leginfo.legislature.ca.gov/faces/codes_displaySection.xhtml?lawCode=RTC&sectionNum=17034.", "title": "us ca code rtc p5"}, "ordinal": 2, "parent_citation_path": "us-ca/statute/rtc/17034", "parent_id": "ef79c4f4-494a-509e-8cb4-32c513512039", "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_format": "html", "source_id": "us-ca-code-rtc-p5", "source_path": "sources/us-ca/statute/2026-07-13-recovery/official-documents/us-ca-code-rtc-p5", "source_url": "https://leginfo.legislature.ca.gov/faces/codes_displaySection.xhtml?lawCode=RTC&sectionNum=17034.", "version": "2026-07-13-recovery"}
